name: As a user, I check export the project type React Native and Nextjs successfully with scenario 1
fullName: JIT-Export-005-Scenario-RN-NJS-login-screen.As a user, I check export the project type React Native and Nextjs successfully with scenario 1

steps.name: Given I am login on staging env by created timestamp project
When I navigate to menu "Mobile app" with submenu "Mobile Editor"
Then I should see Mobile screen display
When I select tab name Pages with index 1
When I add new screen with name jitexpmobile001
When I select screen with name jitexpmobile001
When I select tab list with name "Layers"
When I open Search popup on item value "jitexpmobile001" with index "1"
When I add item "Form" in Search popup to preview mobile editor
When I select item value "Form" with index "1"
When I open Search popup on item value "Form" with index "1"
When I add item "Input" in Search popup to preview mobile editor
When I select item value "Form" with index "1"
When I open Search popup on item value "Form" with index "1"
When I add item "Button" in Search popup with sub menu "Basic" to preview mobile editor
When I select item value "Input" with index "1"
When I toggle off Layout tree header
When I update field label "Label text" of header "TextInput Properties" with value "Jitera Testing label"
When I update field label "Placeholder" of header "TextInput Properties" with value "Jitera Testing place holder"
When I update field label "Placeholder" of header "TextInput Properties" with value "Jitera Testing place holder"
When I select the color for field label "Placeholder Color" of header "TextInput Properties" by inputting the hexcode value "FF0000"
When I select dropdown field label "Keyboard Type" of header "TextInput Properties" with value "Phone"
When I select item value "Button" with index "1"
When I toggle off Layout tree header
When I update field label "Title" of header "Title" with value "Jitera Testing button"
When I update field label "Size" of header "Title" with value "20"
When I select the color for field label "Color" of header "Title" by inputting the hexcode value "FF0000"
When I select checkbox with label "Italic" of header "Title"
When I select checkbox with label "Underline" of header "Title"
When I export project source code for "ReactNative" without option ""
Then I should see project name on exporting popup equal to projectName
When I wait export completely with timeout
Then I should see the exporting is passed
When I confirm Done for exporting popup
When I export project source code for "NextJS" without option ""
Then I should see project name on exporting popup equal to projectName
When I wait export completely with timeout
Then I should see the exporting is passed
